<number box="[1086,1115,298,323]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="52.0">52</number>
preanal) and the following measurements (in mm): total length 
<number box="[564,609,335,359]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="284.0">284</number>
; head length 
<number box="[761,813,335,359]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="21.3">21.3</number>
; trunk length 
<number box="[971,1023,335,359]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="94.7">94.7</number>
; jaw length ca. 
<number box="[1203,1238,335,359]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="8.4">8.4</number>
(the jaw is cut at the rictus on both sides); snout length 
<number box="[586,624,370,395]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="3.6">3.6</number>
; eye diameter 1.0; interorbital width 
