; body depth at gill opening ca. 
<number box="[151,189,406,431]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="5.4">5.4</number>
; and body width at gill opening ca. 
<number box="[586,624,406,431]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="4.6">4.6</number>
. Its dentition was illustrated by Blache and Bauchot (
<figureCitation box="[1217,1315,406,431]" captionStart="FIGURE 7" captionStartId="10.[151,250,1952,1974]" captionTargetBox="[508,1071,217,1908]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[489,1097,193,1930]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURE 7. Dentition of holotype of Apterichtus dunalailai, MNHN 1987 - 0810, 289 mm. Drawn by Corlis Schneider." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/288218/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="57">
Figure 
<number box="[1299,1315,408,431]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="7.0">7</number>
</figureCitation>
, p. 
<number box="[1354,1400,407,431]" pageId="8" pageNumber="57" value="713.0">713</number>
). It has the following cephalic pores: single median interorbital and temporal pores; supraorbital pores 
